text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Darija Jurak and María José Martínez Sánchez won the title, defeating Margarita Gasparyan and Monica Niculescu in the final, 7–5, 2–6, [10–7]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== *Main Draw Bronx Open - Doubles 2019 Doubles
